First of all hello everyone, This will be our first year with limelight 3. Our robot uses navx2, maxSwerve. We want to track Apriltags with Limelight 3. We don’t have much information about this. Some people have done it by uploading photonvision to limelight on the internet or some have done it directly through limelight’s own program. Which one do you think provides easier tracking and which one is more compatible? Also, is there a source for adding it to YAGSL?
Thanks in advance everyone.

We want to track Apriltags with Limelight 3.

just follow the limelight docs and yagsl has addVisionReading() method or something like that.

FRCTEAM9447:

LimelightOS is best and easier for apriltag tracking I think.
